le=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #00cc00;\">1. \u0110\u1ed0I T\u01af\u1ee2NG TUY\u1ec2N SINH<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong>1.1 V\u1ec1 v\u0103n b\u1eb1ng <\/strong><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\">a) Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc <em>(Xem Danh m\u1ee5c ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00fang, ng\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n: Ph\u1ee5 l\u1ee5c 01)<\/em><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt;\u00a0T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00fang: kh\u00f4ng pha\u0309i ho\u0323c b\u00f4\u0309 sung ki\u00ea\u0301n th\u01b0\u0301c;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n: ho\u0323c b\u00f4\u0309 sung ki\u00ea\u0301n th\u01b0\u0301c 15 t\u00edn ch\u1ec9;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; T\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc c\u00e1c ng\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c: ho\u0323c b\u00f4\u0309 sung ki\u00ea\u0301n th\u01b0\u0301c 24 t\u00edn ch\u1ec9.<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">b) Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p<span style=\"color: black;\"> \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc do c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh hi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\"><strong>1.2 V\u1ec1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh \u0111\u00fang, ng\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 thi ngay sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc ng\u00e0nh kh\u00e1c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 02 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 thi.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #ffff00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #00cc00;\">2. PH\u01af\u01a0NG TH\u1ee8C TUY\u1ec2N SINH\u00a0<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\">Thi tuy\u1ec3n <em>(Xem Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh mi\u1ec5n thi ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef: Ph\u1ee5 l\u1ee5c 02)<\/em><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong>M\u00f4n thi: Ti\u00ea\u0301ng Anh, Kinh t\u00ea\u0301 ho\u0323c, Qua\u0309n tri\u0323 ho\u0323c<\/strong>.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #ffff00;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #00cc00;\">3. TH\u1edcI GIAN<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\"><em>Nh\u1eadn h\u1ed3 s\u01a1:<\/em> T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>20\/0<\/strong><strong>1<\/strong><strong>\/202<\/strong><strong>1<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>15<\/strong><strong>\/0<\/strong><strong>4<\/strong><strong>\/202<\/strong><strong>1<\/strong>;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\"><em>Thi tuy\u1ec3n (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn): <\/em>Ng\u00e0y <strong>05, 06\/06\/2021<\/strong>; <em>Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc (d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn)<\/em>: <strong>20\/06\/2021<\/strong>;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\"><em>\u00d4n t\u1eadp, h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5 sung ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c:<\/em> T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y <strong>17\/04\/2021<\/strong> \u0111\u1ebfn <strong>30\/05\/2021<\/strong>.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffff00;\"><span style=\"background-color: #00cc00;\">4. L\u1ed8 TR\u00ccNH H\u1eccC T\u1eacP TO\u00c0N KH\u00d3A<\/span><\/span>\u00a01.5 n\u0103m<\/strong> (<strong>02 h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng <\/strong>v\u00e0<strong> 01 k\u1ef3 h\u1ecdc doanh nh\u00e2n <\/strong>c\u00f9ng chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n <strong>KNV group<\/strong>, t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n <strong>Elite PR school<\/strong> + tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc)<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffff00;\"><span style=\"background-color: #00cc00;\">5. H\u1eccC PH\u00cd, L\u1ec6 PH\u00cd, H\u1eccC B\u1ed4NG<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed: \u00a0\u00a048.000.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ kh\u00f3a<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; H\u1ecdc ph\u00ed h\u1ecdc b\u1ed5 sung ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c: 420.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ 1 t\u00edn ch\u1ec9<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed:<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 H\u1ed3 s\u01a1: mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00d4n thi: 500.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/1 m\u00f4n thi; Thi tuy\u1ec3n: 200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/1 m\u00f4n thi.<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\"><span style=\"color: #212529;\">&gt;&gt; H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng:<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng to\u00e0n ph\u1ea7n: t\u1eb7ng 100% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed to\u00e0n kh\u00f3a;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng b\u00e1n ph\u1ea7n: t\u1eb7ng 50% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed to\u00e0n kh\u00f3a;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng ti\u1ebfp s\u1ee9c t\u00e2n h\u1ecdc vi\u00ean: t\u1eb7ng 1.000.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ 1 hv;\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0H\u1ecdc b\u1ed5ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp: t\u1eb7ng 20% h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed to\u00e0n kh\u00f3a.<\/span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ffff00;\"><span style=\"background-color: #00cc00;\">6. H\u1ed2 S\u01a0<\/span><\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; Phi\u1ebfu \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd d\u1ef1 thi (theo m\u1eabu c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4);<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; B\u1ea3n sao c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc;<\/span><\/span><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Times New Roman,Times,serif;\"><span style=\"background-color: white;\">&gt;&gt; S\u01a1 y\u1ebfu l\u00fd l\u1ecbch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n